### Project: webenc — All 6 phases (Tasks #604-609)
WHATWG Encoding Standard for Python, drop-in replacement for webencodings (92M monthly downloads, abandoned since 2017). Modules: labels.py (~200 WHATWG encoding labels, case-insensitive lookup), bom.py (BOM sniffing for UTF-8/UTF-16BE/UTF-16LE), codecs.py (WebDecoder/WebEncoder with replacement/fatal/html error modes wrapping stdlib codecs), __init__.py (TextDecoder/TextEncoder web-platform APIs, lookup()), compat.py (webencodings shim: Encoding, decode, encode, iter_decode, iter_encode). Zero deps, Python 3.10+, MIT, py.typed. 114 tests pass, mypy --strict clean, CI green.

